dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:59:45.000Z","msg":"成日見人係度洗版，日日小組送頭，乜文宣都無哂，唔知做乜鳩。<br />\n<br />\n文宣方向建議如下 : <br />\n1. 集中宣傳建制沒為港人發聲及其他<br />\n2. 全球登報，聲援各地港人<br />\n3. 宣傳8月5日三罷<br />\n4. 重新五點訴求<br />\n5. 平反香港對中國的重要性，自由民主才有利經濟。香港佔中國外資 70%<br />\n6. 宣傳 run and hit, 強烈譴責戀戰行為<br />\n7. 除暴Go<br />\n8. 宣傳年輕一代入獄、移民，所有藍絲家長以後自己照顧自己，共享大灣區榮耀。<br />\n9. 心經簡林、蛇陣長輩圖<br />\n10. 整合多天以後衝擊材料，如醫療系統病人資料不保密、白衣人事、件、濫權、煙花<br />\n11. 支持星火等。。。捐款 (每次行動，比人拉多1x個都死啦。唔該行動前好好考慮法律支援費用仲有幾多係度可以燒)<br />\n12. 其他"},{"pid":"cf0bb980b357cfb427e7d1f15f685d18e531b4d9","tid":1384961,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ce86dd9fd80e6e49127cb6cbece044aeb78b107","tid":1384961,"uid":11854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:36:35.000Z","msg":"等車無野做米幫下手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:03:19.000Z","msg":"倒不如&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmrTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=6a36cd44\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721</a>"},{"pid":"0c75ac3f878d4d91ef0cf20686ae706b8c503bf1","tid":1384961,"uid":280547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:15:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9cd88b6449d3aacd6818e8546e54b3087eb1b508","tid":1384961,"uid":223198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec971723911589d84c05d5dc9dc1f884dee0c419","tid":1384961,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re